Sentencas: The mechanical properties of anode materials play an important role in the reliability and durability of solid oxide fuel cells operating at high temperatures in a reducing environment.
Titulo: Microstructure and mechanical properties of Ni/10 mol% Sc2O3-1 mol% CeO2-ZrO2 cermet anode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this paper, we produced the results of the mechanical properties investigation of Ni/10 mol% Sc2O3-1 mol% CeO2-ZrO2 cermet anodes.
Titulo: Microstructure and mechanical properties of Ni/10 mol% Sc2O3-1 mol% CeO2-ZrO2 cermet anode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Young's modulus as well as strength and fracture toughness of non-reduced and reduced anodes has been measured, both at room and at high temperatures.
Titulo: Microstructure and mechanical properties of Ni/10 mol% Sc2O3-1 mol% CeO2-ZrO2 cermet anode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: High temperature experiments were performed in the reducing environment of forming gas.
Titulo: Microstructure and mechanical properties of Ni/10 mol% Sc2O3-1 mol% CeO2-ZrO2 cermet anode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It is shown that while at 700 degrees C and 800 degrees C, the anode specimens exhibited purely elastic deformation and brittle fracture, a brittle-to-ductile transition occurred for heating above 800 degrees C and the anode deformed plastically at 900 degrees C. Fractography of the anode specimens were performed to identify the fracture modes of anodes tested at different temperatures.
Titulo: Microstructure and mechanical properties of Ni/10 mol% Sc2O3-1 mol% CeO2-ZrO2 cermet anode for solid oxide fuel cells
